---
title: Home
layout: layouts/base.njk
seo:
  title: "Developer Roadmaps"
  description: "Community driven roadmaps, articles and guides for developers to grow in their career."
sitemap:
  priority: 1
  changefreq: monthly
tags:
  - main-sitemap
---

<div class='mb-32'>
  <div class='my-8'>
    <h1 class='text-2xl mb-1 font-bold'>Developer Roadmaps</h1>
    <hr class='border border-gray-800 my-2' />
    <p><span class='font-semibold'>roadmap.sh</span> is a community effort to create roadmaps, guides and other
      educational content to help guide the developers in picking up the path and guide their learnings.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class='text-lg font-bold mb-2'>Role based</h2>
  <ul class='mb-5 grid grid-cols-4 gap-2'>
    {% for roadmap in collections['roleRoadmaps'] %}
      <li>
        <a class='bg-gray-200 p-3 font-medium block no-underline text-black hover:bg-gray-300 rounded-md'
           href='{{ roadmap.data.permalink }}'>
          {{ roadmap.data.title }}
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  <h2 class='text-lg font-bold mb-2'>Skill based</h2>
  <ul class='mb-5 grid grid-cols-4 gap-2'>
    {% for roadmap in collections['skillRoadmaps'] %}
      <li>
        <a class='bg-gray-200 p-3 font-medium block no-underline text-black hover:bg-gray-300 rounded-md'
           href='{{ roadmap.data.permalink }}'>
          {{ roadmap.data.title }}
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  <div class='my-8'>
    <h1 class='text-2xl mb-1 font-bold'>Videos</h1>
    <hr class='border border-gray-800 mt-2 mb-3' />
    <ul class='mb-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-1'>
      {% for video in (collections['video'] | reverse).slice(0, 10) %}
        <li>
          <a class='no-underline text-blue-800 hover:text-red-700 flex justify-between' href={{ video.data.page.url }}>
            {{ video.data.title }} <span class='capitalize text-gray-600'>{{ video.data.duration }}</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <a href='/videos' class='p-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300'>All Videos</a>
  </div>

  <div class='my-8'>
    <h1 class='text-2xl mb-1 font-bold'>Guides</h1>
    <hr class='border border-gray-800 mt-2 mb-3' />
    <ul class='mb-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-1'>
      {% for guide in (collections['guide'] | reverse).slice(0, 10) %}
        <li>
          <a class='no-underline text-blue-800 hover:text-red-700 flex justify-between' href={{ guide.data.page.url }}>
            {{ guide.data.title }} <span class='capitalize text-gray-600'>{{ guide.data.type }}</span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <a href='/guides' class='p-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300'>All Guides</a>
  </div>

</div>
